</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0171-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0171-fn-0001">1</a>
	
   <p>GW apparently enclosed <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0163" class="document">his letter to Reed of 31 January</a>. Reeds letter to GW of 21 Jan. has not been found.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0171-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0171-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0200" class="document">GW to Hancock, 9 Feb. 1776</a> (second letter).</p>

</div>
